{"tid":1229131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人你仲忍？","createTime":"2019-06-15T22:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T22:24:59.000Z","uid":43414,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3304e0aacd8c3c4b50b65bb66804353e88c03015","tid":1229131,"uid":43414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T22:19:13.000Z","msg":"係！你仲要忍！！<br />\n唔係叫你忍一世<br />\n只係16號呢日！<br />\n今日遊行有大有細，有老有嫩<br />\n所以絕對唔適合衝突！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意到有人喺義士死後不斷鼓吹今日要衝<br />\n千祈唔好上當！<br />\n仲有鼓吹要港獨嘅<br />\n我話你聽，時機未到！<br />\n呢個時候打住港獨嘅旗號只會令中間溫和派反感<br />\n到時只會阻止唔到送中<br />\n正中柒婆下懷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意翻！<br />\n今日遊行訴求只係<br />\n<br />\n1. 遣責警方暴力鎮壓市民<br />\n2. 撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n3. 柒婆下台<br />\n<br />\n最後，香港人團結！<br />\n<br />\n今日，黑衫白花，維園見！"},{"pid":"1f679ac67e6d99295cf47321a325b39184157e8b","tid":1229131,"uid":43414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T22:24:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"06f843431b4fd151d517d2cfecea4b2c239412c8","tid":1229131,"uid":43414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T22:24:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cb0f7e57d76d619ccf193898e7eb3ee6b51cabca","tid":1229131,"uid":43414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T22:24:59.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}